      "text": "18. Simejus Ela Dehls biia\\neekſch Benjamina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "19. Gebers Urus Dehls biia\\neekſch Gileadas/ tahs Semmes\\nSiona ta Amoriters Kehnixa/\\nun Oga ta Kehnixa no Bahsa-\\nna Semmê/ un biia tas weenigs\\nPawaldneeks/kastai Semnê biia.\n"
