    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "20. Juhda un Israels biia\\ndauds/ tik dauds ta Similtis/ kas\\nJuhr-Malli irr/ tee ehde un dseh-\\nre/ un preezajahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "21. Un Salamans wardija\\npahr wiſſahm Walſtibahn/ no\\ntahs Uppeß Wilisteru Semmê/\\nlihds tai Egiptes Rohbeschai/ tee\\natneffe Dahwanas/ un kalpoja\\nSalamanam wiſſa winnaMuh-\\nschâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "22. Un Salamana Barriba\\nus weenu Deenu biia trihsdes-\\nmits Kori Kweefchu-Milti/fesch-\\ndesmits Kori zitti Milti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "23. Defunits barrotti Wehr-\\nfchi/ un diwidefunits Wehrſchi/\\nno Gannibas/ un ſints Awis/\\nbes Erſcheem un Stirnehm/ un\\nMescha-Kasahin un barroteein\\nLohpeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "24. Jo wiſſch wardija pahr\\nwiſſahm Weetahtm/ tas ſchat puts\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Uppes biia/ no Tiwsas lihds Ga-\\nsat/ pahr wiſſeem Kehnineei\\ntchaipufs Uppes. Un winnan\\nbiia Meers no wiſſeem winna\\nApkahrtajeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "25. Un Juhda un Israels diſi\\nwoja ar Meeru/ikkatrs appakſc\\nfawa Wihna-Kohka un appakſc\\ntawa Wihges-Kohka/no Danna\\nlihds Bersebai/ wiſſa Salanna\\nka Muhschâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "26. Un Salamanam biji ticheſt\\ndefinitis tuhkſtoschi Rattu-Sir\\ngu Stellingi/ un divipadeſimit\\ntuhkſtoschi Jahtneeki.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "27. Un tee Pawaldneeki i\\nkatrs fawa Mehnefi apkohe t\\nkas pee ta Kehnixa Salamanu/ un wiſſus\\nkas pee ta Kehnixa Salamanu\\nGalda ehde/ teem ne truhke n\\nneeka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "28. Un tohs Meeschus un Sal-\\nnius preekſch teem Sirgeem/ un\\ntschakleem Kameeteem nefte tee\\ntai Weeta/ kur ta biia (fataiſi-\\nta)/ ikkatrs pehz fawaß Paweh-\\nlefchanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "29. Un Deews dewe Salama-\\naam Gudribu/ un lohti dauds\\nSapratchanas/ un drohſchn Sir-\\ndi ta Smiltis/ kas Juhr-Mal-\\nlâ irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "30. Un Salamana Gudriba\\nbiia leelaka ne ka wiſſu Behrnu\\nprett Rihteem/ un wiſſu Egipte-\\nru Gudriba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "31. Un wiſſch biia gudrafs\\nne ka wiſſi Zilwekti/ ne ka Getans\\ntas Eſrätteris/ un Gemans/ un\\nRalkals/ un Dardus Madus\\nDehli.\n"
    }
